data.description: Beautiful 2 story home in Bridlewood Park subdivision! This 4 bed 3 bath house has been recently rehabbed and has plenty of room to spare!  Brand new luxury vinyl plank and carpet installed throughout house! New Roof installed November 2023!  Fresh coat of interior paint gives the home a fresh new look!  Downstairs you will find the formal dining room and spacious living room with a cozy stacked stone corner fireplace. Luxury open kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, large cabinets and walk-in pantry! As you make your way upstairs you will find a HUGE game/media/flex family room with TV already mounted! Generous primary bedroom / bathroom has extended closet for plenty of storage! Outside is a large partially covered wooden deck perfect for relaxing or entertaining! Neighborhood has fun playground, basketball court and covered pavilion!  Home close to shopping and restaurants, I35 and Loop 1604 access, as well as Randolph AFB and Ft. Sam AFB.  What more could you ask for!
